            {
              "message": "AC-02 accepts `README.md` at ≤90 lines, but CN-01 in the same spec says Tier 1 files, explicitly including `README.md`, must be ≤80 lines. That means an 81-90 line README would satisfy the acceptance criterion while violating the plan's stated Tier 1 constraint.",
